en: Traditional packaging boxes are often made of materials like tin, paper, or plastic. en: Wrinkled Skin and Thin Peel Are My Signature

Because our dragon fruit is grown on tropical highland farms with ample sunlight, it naturally thrives under full exposure to sunlight and rain.
